import React, { Component } from 'react'; import './App.css'; import { profile1 } from './profileData'; class App extends Component { render() { console.log("profile1", profile1); return (
{profile1.map(item => (
{item.name}
{item.role}
{item.key1}
{item.description1}
{item.key2}
{item.description2}
{item.key3}
{item.description3}
{item.key4}
{item.description4}
{item.key5}
{item.description5}
{item.key6}
{item.description6}
{item.key7}
{item.description7}
{item.key8}
{item.description8}
))}
) } } export default App;
